gomodel:SYNGO_2947  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Fig.4: \"Rab17 co-localizes with Syntaxin-4 in the dendritic shaft, tip, and spine\"\n\nNote: Rab17 is in this paper shown to transport Stx4 from the cell soma to the dendrites thereby influencing KAR membrane levels.. Experimental description: - \"At 8 DIV, mouse hippocampal neurons were co-transfected w...\"\n- Overexpressed Rab17 is of mouse species (traced back via blast analsysis of primer sequence ATGGCGCAGGCTGCTGG)" ;
